===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# {{lb|zh|literary}} to [[exist]]
#: {{zh-co|共存|to coexist}}
# to [[cherish]]; to [[harbor]]
#: {{zh-co|存心|to harbour intentions}}
#: {{zh-co|存 著[着]{zhe} 希望|to cherish hopes}}
#: {{zh-q|^孟子 曰：「君子 所 以 異 於 人 者，以 其 存 心 也。君子 以 仁 存 心，以 禮 存 心。」|Mencius said, 'That whereby the superior man is distinguished from other men is what he '''preserves''' in his heart - namely, benevolence and propriety.'|ref=Mencius}}
# to [[leave]] with; to [[check]]
#: {{zh-co|存 行李|to check luggage}}
# to [[deposit]]
#: {{zh-co|存 在 銀行{háng}|to deposit in a bank}}
# to [[remain]] on [[balance]]; to be in [[stock]]
#: {{zh-co|存 兩 千 元|to remain 2,000 yuan on balance}}
# to [[accumulate]]; to [[collect]]
#: {{zh-co|坑 裡 存 了 水|water accumulated in the pit}}
# to [[store]]; to [[keep]]; to [[save]]
#: {{zh-co|存糧|to store up grain}}
#: {{zh-co|存款|financial savings}}
#: {{zh-co|存 文件|to save the file}}
# [[stock]]; [[reserve]]
#: {{zh-co|庫存|stock; reserve}}
# {{lb|zh|literary|archaic}} to [[call on]], to [[inquire]]; to show [[concern]]; to offer [[comfort]] 
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien}} to [[modest]]ly [[concede]]; to [[humbly]] [[decline]]
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien}} to [[prepare]] in [[advance]]; to [[anticipate]] [[beforehand]]

